华南海鲜市场“潜伏”的一家四口被隔离，带头的“老顾”找到了。
South China seafood market "latent" a family of four people was isolated, led by "old care" found.
隗延章。
Kui Yanzhang.
中国新闻周刊                      。
China News Weekly.
